  "detailed_description": "<h1>#NOTICE</h1><p>ㅍHello. This is Leaguemanager.<br><br>League Manager 2022 will be closed on 13 Jan 2023. <br>Thank you for your surpot, and League Manager 2023 is on Early Access. <br><br>Thank you</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>1. Choose the team you want!</strong><br><br>The world’s best team is ready for you<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/d7c26d1372d41ec242212200ffc0de47.poster.avif?t=1673620300\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/d7c26d1372d41ec242212200ffc0de47.webm?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/d7c26d1372d41ec242212200ffc0de47.mp4?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. Various systems of management</strong><br><br>Make the best game with various and detailed managing systems.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3692d73247c10f3392bc377151106bf9.poster.avif?t=1673620300\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3692d73247c10f3392bc377151106bf9.webm?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3692d73247c10f3392bc377151106bf9.mp4?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3. this game provides experience based on reality (teams, player, league etc...)</strong><br><br>Lead the legendary players to get the best results in the game which is almost like real<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3397b8cfc8d1f0871d98489a3675790d.poster.avif?t=1673620300\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3397b8cfc8d1f0871d98489a3675790d.webm?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/3397b8cfc8d1f0871d98489a3675790d.mp4?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4. Observing your game of team in detail</strong><br><br>Watch the game in detail, analyze the results, and make a legendary team.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/45d81446c595086730b7d64e56a91566.poster.avif?t=1673620300\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/45d81446c595086730b7d64e56a91566.webm?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745400/extras/45d81446c595086730b7d64e56a91566.mp4?t=1673620300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
